	   <tr><td colspan=2>A warrior with this shield will not hold agro well at all, but if they pick up the FB 3 one from HoH or the FB4 one from BoT it would be very easy to maintain agro.. there is rumored to be up to FB7 shields out there. <br><br>I have the FB3 one from HoH and using it and a BoC in exp groups I hold agro well, but will loose it to a rogue in the beginning if they score a huge BS, your mileage may vary.<br><br>One thing to keep in mind as a warrior, when using these new shields, since your using only 1 weapon you take fewer riposte hits while still getting added agro from the shield effect.. down side is, if your a number cruncher your dps falls thru the floor.. but using a shield is not about DPS it's about defense<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Wed Mar 19 07:26:18 2003</em><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
